Below is a much simpler Angular chat implementation (still production-friendly) that supports:

✅ Open chat button
✅ Minimize / maximize / close
✅ Send message
✅ File upload
✅ Model selection
✅ Chat history (sessions)
✅ Settings panel
✅ Colored chat bubbles
✅ Simple REST API calls

This version uses only 2 components + 1 service, making it very easy to integrate into an existing Angular 19 enterprise application.

